{"rating_score": "10.0", "rating_badge": "\u7121\u8207\u502b\u6bd4", "description": "The room is very spacious and bright. The location is very convenient,  it is next to Tsim Sha Tsui East MTR station, it is very easy going everywhere. There are many shopping, eating and drinking places around. The hotel provides many quality amenities/toiletries. Our king bed is very comfy.  The seaview room has a very nice harbour view. The doormen, porters and receptionists are very helpful.  We highly recommend this hotel. ", "date": "2019\u5e7409\u670804\u65e5\u8a55\u50f9"}
{"rating_score": "8.0", "rating_badge": "\u5fc3\u6c34\u4e4b\u9078", "description": "The service overall us good except the service in the Tapas Bar is a bit slow. Waited long time and had to signalled to the waiter/waitress to come taking our order.  ", "date": "2019\u5e7408\u670830\u65e5\u8a55\u50f9"}
{"rating_score": "10.0", "rating_badge": "\u7121\u8207\u502b\u6bd4", "description": "We upgraded to harbor view room. The room was amazing, big, beautiful, and unforgettable views.  We love the location.", "date": "2019\u5e7408\u670829\u65e5\u8a55\u50f9"}
{"rating_score": "8.0", "rating_badge": "\u5fc3\u6c34\u4e4b\u9078", "description": "My favorite hotel in HK because of the friendly and accommodating staff and the location due to accessibility to public transportation and the availability of numerous restaurants.", "date": "2019\u5e7408\u670826\u65e5\u8a55\u50f9"}
{"rating_score": "8.0", "rating_badge": "\u5fc3\u6c34\u4e4b\u9078", "description": "We used to live in HK and would prefer the location of Shangrila due to the accessibility to public transportation and the availability of so many restaurants around the area.", "date": "2019\u5e7408\u670827\u65e5\u8a55\u50f9"}
{"rating_score": "8.0", "rating_badge": "\u5fc3\u6c34\u4e4b\u9078", "description": "Classic Nice hotel, good location, the staff is friendly", "date": "2019\u5e7408\u670828\u65e5\u8a55\u50f9"}
{"rating_score": "6.0", "rating_badge": "\u826f\u597d", "description": "Disappointed by the rather outdated decor and room condition of a Shangri-La establishment. Request for late checkout was met with, \u201cwe\u2019ll charge you half day rates\u201d. Never happened with Intercontinental or Marriott hotels I\u2019ve put up at. Location is good though as it is accessible to a lot of eateries and convenient to move around.", "date": "2019\u5e7408\u670823\u65e5\u8a55\u50f9"}
{"rating_score": "8.0", "rating_badge": "\u5fc3\u6c34\u4e4b\u9078", "description": "Great location, clean, very comfortable bed and great room with good amenities, the Kowloon Shangrii-La is just what the doctor ordered after a long, international flight.  \n\nMy room was extremely quiet with shutters and drapes which keep it nice and dark for sleeping in.  \n\nThe king sized bed was fantastic, the bathroom had both a bathtub and a great shower with wonderful water pressure and hot water.\n\nThe mini bar was nice and well stocked.  I ordered room service and the food was above average.\n\nThe hotel is a bit pricey, but sometimes you get what you pay for.  \n\nThere could be more premium movie channels (there were none from my experience).", "date": "2019\u5e7408\u670825\u65e5\u8a55\u50f9"}
{"rating_score": "10.0", "rating_badge": "\u7121\u8207\u502b\u6bd4", "description": "An excellent hotel ! We were very happy and will definitely make this our choice for our next visit to Hong Kong.", "date": "2019\u5e7408\u670819\u65e5\u8a55\u50f9"}
